                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 17192/1A.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Ambassador <persName type="to">Griscom</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-12-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 30, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The National Red Cross will cable to-morrow for account of the Italian Red Cross
                    $50,000 for the relief of the earthquake sufferers.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bacon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
